{"tid":1160824,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Mesh wifi 擺位問題","createTime":"2019-05-18T17:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T18:03:50.000Z","uid":53559,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa798e1fd2378ddb75a21953e5023664857019a8","tid":1160824,"uid":53559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩裝左光纖1000M上網, 諗住扔撚左原本個垃圾home plug, 再買左個tp-link m5 諗住我間尾房都可以高清睇a片打個靚j <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知我間尾房都裝左m5之後上網都係得60mb左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同之前用homeplug冇分別, 有冇巴打幫手睇睇可以點擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijzxreN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijzxreN.jpg&h=115ae37b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n係張圖到綠點係我router (主m5)個位置, 收到3xx mb (綠點後面係主力牆)<br />\n企係走廊1 既位置仲收到2xx~3xx mb, 但係去到2(我間房門口)果陣已經趺到去60mb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紅點係我間房電腦既位置, 擺左子m5要黎插lan線落部電腦到, 點知都係最盡得60mb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我試過將子m5 放中間房, 結果尾房wifi都係收到得60mb<br />\n有冇巴打可以教我點set <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 還是我要買多一個m5 放中間房先連貫到成間屋上網有3xx mb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fdd6a700f809380a34d3577c5b3f240d7fce1e","tid":1160824,"uid":176472,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T17:23:33.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚柒大間屋 嬲 上一頁 拜鳩拜"},{"pid":"d28eab128e78cf3196cd7a64333a97c9af3f8554","tid":1160824,"uid":29540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"10fdd6a700f809380a34d3577c5b3f240d7fce1e","tid":1160824,"uid":176472,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T17:23:33.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚柒大間屋 嬲 上一頁 拜鳩拜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T17:25:20.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"212da122185e2e99fce5c1a3dc68ef7289d7941b","tid":1160824,"uid":53559,"like":2